{"tid":1768234,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[再嚟] 美眾議院通過法案要求制裁涉鎮壓維族人的中國高級官員","createTime":"2019-12-04T02:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T03:03:40.000Z","uid":299537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f26656553546ac02f554007b3840f292ddd36f72","tid":1768234,"uid":299537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T02:45:13.000Z","msg":"美國眾議院通過《2019年維吾爾人權政策法案》，要求國務院一年內提交報告，審視中國新疆維吾爾族的人權狀況，並對鎮壓維吾爾人的中國高級官員實施制裁。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院以407票贊成、1票反對，壓倒性通過法案，眾議院議長波洛西譴責中國當局策劃鎮壓新疆維吾爾人的行動，包括監視、單獨囚禁、毆打和強迫絕育等，國會正採取重要行動，制止北京的嚴重侵犯行為。<br />\n<br />\n眾議院通過的法案，是參議院法案的修訂版，法案增加部份條款，要求總統特朗普制裁鎮壓維吾爾族的中國官員，並限制出口可能用於間諜或控制維吾爾人的通訊設備。<br />\n<br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495876-20191204.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495876-20191204.htm&d=sHvBfS5bCv0nfD6zjI7mDS%2B7EDXmwg1SXj7S5MqlT1o%3D&h=c44af45e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1495876-20191204.htm&h=b4ae6f37\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1495876-20191204.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n有請小鳳姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce06edb81778994a1327cf9acd92dc7b133a4be9","tid":1768234,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T02:48:23.000Z","msg":"DJI應該玩完"},{"pid":"2813cdc6f1eba6f85b963ec61c8c7b4d2b1fb7d7","tid":1768234,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T03:03:40.000Z","msg":"維吾爾人權政策法過左！上twitter 賀一賀佢！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768124\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768124</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}